Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向您推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只需隨意按幾個號碼
